WEBVTT

00:00:02.151 --> 00:00:03.568
By raising your hand,

00:00:03.592 --> 00:00:07.207
how many of you know
at least one person on the screen?

00:00:08.367 --> 00:00:10.234
Wow, it's almost a full house.

00:00:10.258 --> 00:00:12.815
It's true, they are very famous
in their fields.

00:00:12.839 --> 00:00:15.834
And do you know what
all of them have in common?

00:00:15.858 --> 00:00:18.778
They all died of pancreatic cancer.

00:00:18.802 --> 00:00:21.310
However, although it's very,
very sad this news,

00:00:21.334 --> 00:00:24.098
it's also thanks to their personal stories

00:00:24.122 --> 00:00:28.243
that we have raised awareness
of how lethal this disease can be.

00:00:28.267 --> 00:00:31.643
It's become the third cause
of cancer deaths,